node.text:
Today is a very special day to me, today is the day where I can show you what do i have been working on with @standrecoverycentre 

This is my story. Thank you for watching. 

If you could share to as many people as possible it would mean the world to me. Let’s try our best as a team to get this to as many people as possible! You never know who needs our help! 

Please donate🤍  @standrecoverycentre @standrecoverycentre @standrecoverycentre
